      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64]{Envoy Improvisation}</p>\n<p>Whenever you’re reduced to 0 Hit Points, as a reaction before gaining the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.4MxAK5uS0zMNWhUK]{Dying} condition, you can immediately use any one of your envoy improvisations that can be used as a standard action, move action, or reaction. Once you have used this improvisation, you can’t use this ability again until you have regained Stamina Points following a 10-minute rest.</p>"
